        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7784_p1"> <note type="com" xml:id="K_7784_c0">Nachträglicher Stempel oben rechts auf Seite 1 mit von dritter Hand eingetragener Nummer: <orig>Gotthardbahn | <date when="1872-07-27">27 JULI 1872</date>. | <choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> 2190.</orig> – Nachträgliche Inhaltsangabe oben links auf Seite 1 von dritter Hand: <orig>Auskunftsgesuch über eine Offerte, <choice><abbr>betr.</abbr><expan>betreffend</expan></choice> Uebernahme des großen Tunnels. | II <choice><abbr>Dep.</abbr><expan>Departement</expan></choice> </orig> – Nachträgliche Notiz unten rechts von dritter Hand: <orig><choice><abbr>Prot.</abbr><expan>Protokoll</expan></choice> <date when="1872-07-17">17. <hi>VII.</hi> 72</date>. <choice><abbr>N.</abbr><expan>Nummer</expan></choice> 580.</orig> </note> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">THE MACHINE TUNNELLING COMPANY, LIMITED.
<lb xml:id="p1-l2"/> 2. Westminster Chambers,
            <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>Victoria Street, <choice><abbr>S.W.</abbr><expan>SouthWest (Südwesten)</expan></choice> </hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7784_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="London (UK)">London</placeName>
          </hi>
          <date when="1872-07-08">8<hi rend="sup">th</hi> July <hi rend="printed">187</hi>2</date>
        </p>
      </div>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7784_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>
          <choice><abbr>Mons<hi rend="sup">r</hi> </abbr><expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan></choice> Escher 
         <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/><add><choice><abbr>etc.</abbr><expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan></choice> </add> – <add><choice><abbr>etc.</abbr><expan>et cetera (und anderes)</expan></choice> </add></p> 
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7784_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>Sir,</p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>At a recent interview with
        <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/><choice><abbr>M.</abbr><expan>Mister (Herr)</expan></choice> <persName key="Gerwig Robert">Gerwig</persName> at <placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName>, I was told
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>by that <persName key="Gerwig Robert">gentleman</persName> that I must
        <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>apply to you for information 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>as to the conditions under
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>which you wish our offer to be
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>submitted for the Completion
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>of the <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gothard</placeName> works. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>Up to the present time,
        <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>we are ignorant as to the
        <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>caution money you require.
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>The mode in which payment 
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>will be made, both for
        <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>work done &amp; plant put
        <pb n="2"/><lb xml:id="p2-l1"/>on the ground, and many other
        <lb xml:id="p2-l2"/>points, which it is essential
        <lb xml:id="p2-l3"/>we should know. –</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7784_p7"><lb xml:id="p2-l4"/>I shall be obliged if you will
        <lb xml:id="p2-l5"/>give me the fullest &amp; earliest
        <lb xml:id="p2-l6"/>information in order that no
        <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>delay may arise from our
        <lb xml:id="p2-l8"/>having to communicate further
        <lb xml:id="p2-l9"/>upon these points.</p>
      <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7784_p8"><lb xml:id="p2-l10"/>I am.</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7784_p9"><lb xml:id="p2-l11"/>Sir.
        <lb xml:id="p2-l12"/>Yours, <choice><abbr>obed<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr><expan>obedient (ergeben)</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>S.</abbr><expan>Servant (Diener)</expan></choice> </p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7784_p10"><lb xml:id="p2-l13"/>Fred Beaumont
        <lb xml:id="p2-l14"/>Chairman of the Machine
        <lb xml:id="p2-l15"/>Tunnelling <choice><abbr>Co<hi rend="sup">y</hi> </abbr><expan>Company (Gesellschaft)</expan></choice> Limited </p></div>
